Package: whisper
Title: Native R Torch Implementation of OpenAI Whisper
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "troy@cornball.ai")
Description: Speech-to-text transcription using a native R torch implementation
    of OpenAI's Whisper model. Supports multiple model sizes from tiny (39M params)
    to large-v3 (1.5B params). Provides automatic speech recognition with optional
    language detection and timestamp generation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    torch,
    av,
    jsonlite,
    hfhub
Suggests:
    safetensors,
    tinytest
